 The advantage of this is that the eigendecomposition of 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 is readily calculated as part of the evolution of the system, rather than
 having to be calculated separately at each time step.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It should be noted that the right hand side of 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "eq:dq/dt"

\end_inset

 is undefined when 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{i}=\lambda_{j}$
\end_inset

